"{\"uid\": \"kgns.tv-2024-08-02-jennifer-lozanos-olympic-journey-ends-defeat-laredos-pride-remains\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"LAREDO, Tex.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 12, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 6, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nuevo_Laredo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.003254828672512e-16, \"text\": \"LAREDO\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nuevo_Laredo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nuevo_Laredo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(KGNS) - Laredo can now claim to have had an Olympian compete for Team USA, as Jennifer \\\"La Traviesa\\\" Lozano stepped into the ring Thursday, August 1, at the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 13, \"to\": 183, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 58, \"end\": 66, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999667393535148, \"rank\": 3.326042864487226e-05, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 79, \"end\": 87, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9701314801339801, \"rank\": 0.01706747742531692, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From the opening bell, Lozano appeared uneasy, possibly due to her long layoff and the bright lights of the Olympic stage.\", \"from\": 185, \"to\": 307, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her Finnish opponent had a clear size advantage, which Lozano struggled to overcome.\", \"from\": 308, \"to\": 392, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 312, \"end\": 319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland\", \"score\": 0.940841479593201, \"rank\": 0.04191261118151036, \"text\": \"Finnish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Throughout the first round, the Finnish boxer used her length effectively, keeping Lozano at bay and making it difficult for her to score.\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 532, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 426, \"end\": 433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland\", \"score\": 0.940841479593201, \"rank\": 0.04191261118151036, \"text\": \"Finnish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lozano's troubles continued into the second round, where she again struggled to generate offense and lost the round.\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 649, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Entering the final round, Lozano needed a substantial comeback to advance.\", \"from\": 651, \"to\": 725, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite a determined effort, the judges awarded the victory to her opponent, ending Lozano's Olympic aspirations.\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 839, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The defeat was met with a wave of support from Laredo, where watch parties and social media buzzed with pride for their Olympian.\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 970, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 888, \"end\": 894, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nuevo_Laredo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.003254828672512e-16, \"text\": \"Laredo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nuevo_Laredo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nuevo_Laredo\"}, {\"begin\": 961, \"end\": 969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999667393535148, \"rank\": 3.326042864487226e-05, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Residents gathered to cheer on Lozano, regardless of the outcome.\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 1036, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dr. Victor Trevino, the mayor of Laredo, expressed his honor at Lozano's participation.\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1125, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1042, \"end\": 1048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Newman\", \"score\": 0.8190165177815306, \"rank\": 0.21635705549579165, \"text\": \"Victor\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Newman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Newman\"}, {\"begin\": 1071, \"end\": 1077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nuevo_Laredo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.003254828672512e-16, \"text\": \"Laredo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nuevo_Laredo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nuevo_Laredo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is important because she represents Laredo as one of our best.\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1166, \"end\": 1172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nuevo_Laredo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.003254828672512e-16, \"text\": \"Laredo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nuevo_Laredo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nuevo_Laredo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have good talent here.\\\"\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1219, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jamie Moyer, a professor at TAMIU, praised Lozano's prospects.\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1221, \"end\": 1232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamie_Moyer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jamie Moyer\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamie_Moyer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamie_Moyer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She's on the Olympic team, which means she's one of the best in the country.\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1361, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She certainly has a career ahead of her.\\\"\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1403, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the sting of defeat, Lozano's close friends remain supportive.\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1475, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have been waiting for this moment,\\\" said Brenda Gutierrez.\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1538, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1521, \"end\": 1527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brenda_Barrett\", \"score\": 0.9999569240829899, \"rank\": 4.271646563313035e-05, \"text\": \"Brenda\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brenda_Barrett\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brenda_Barrett\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She has made her dreams come true.\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1574, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have seen it all from the very beginning.\\\"\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1619, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cristina Ramos added, \\\"I am a little sad, but I know Jenny is going to come through with this.\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1715, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1621, \"end\": 1635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cristina_Ramos-Jalasco\", \"score\": 0.9999999877361462, \"rank\": 1.2263797702177574e-08, \"text\": \"Cristina Ramos\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cristina_Ramos-Jalasco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cristina_Ramos-Jalasco\"}, {\"begin\": 1674, \"end\": 1679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Boyd\", \"score\": 0.9999999500173556, \"rank\": 4.929399560309695e-08, \"text\": \"Jenny\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Boyd\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Boyd\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She is going to take this as something to learn from.\\\"\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1770, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Support for Lozano continues to grow.\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1809, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yalitza Howard, a supporter, emphasized the importance of backing her.\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1880, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1818, \"end\": 1824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Howard\", \"score\": 0.9716909448554494, \"rank\": 0.022642830016846697, \"text\": \"Howard\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Howard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Howard\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's important to follow her journey and support her in ways we can.\\\"\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 1951, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paulo Lozano, another supporter, highlighted the significance of Lozano's achievement.\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 2039, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's very important for them to see that if you are passionate and determined, you can achieve significant goals, like going to the Olympics and putting Laredo on the map.\\\"\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2213, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2194, \"end\": 2200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nuevo_Laredo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.003254828672512e-16, \"text\": \"Laredo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nuevo_Laredo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nuevo_Laredo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Though Lozano will return home without a gold medal, she will come back knowing she gave her all.\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2312, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While she is not scheduled to fight again in Paris, Lozano is expected back in Laredo in about a week and a half.\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2426, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2358, \"end\": 2363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998687826606, \"rank\": 1.312173323233298e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2392, \"end\": 2398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nuevo_Laredo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.003254828672512e-16, \"text\": \"Laredo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nuevo_Laredo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nuevo_Laredo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She may consider a return to Team USA for the 2028 Olympics in Los Angeles or explore turning professional.\", \"from\": 2427, \"to\": 2534, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2456, \"end\": 2464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9701314801339801, \"rank\": 0.01706747742531692, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2490, \"end\": 2501, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999346018761, \"rank\": 5.991733885157646e-08, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more headlines, clickhere.\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2566, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright 2024 KGNS.\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\": 2588, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2583, \"end\": 2587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KGNS-TV\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"KGNS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KGNS-TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KGNS-TV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2609, \"entities\": []}]}"